column1: Engineer will input A, B, C in command line to start the program.
The engineer will also be able to input A, B, C in scientific notation to start the program.
The engineers will receive real roots only.
The engineers will be told if double or single solution root.
The engineers will input and receive IEEE single precision floating point numbers.
The engineers will receive a warning if they input numbers with too many decimal places
The engineers will receive a warning if the output has been truncated or rounded.
